### ========================================
### Movie Service — HTTP Requests
### ========================================
### Use com IntelliJ HTTP Client ou REST Client do VS Code

### --- Auth ---

### Login (obter token JWT)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@movie.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Login Admin
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@movie.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### --- Movies ---

### Buscar filmes por texto
GET http://localhost:8080/api/movies/search?query=Matrix&page=1

### Buscar filmes populares
GET http://localhost:8080/api/movies/popular?page=1

### Detalhes de um filme (Matrix = 603)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/movies/603

### --- Favoritos ---

### Favoritar filme (Matrix = 603)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/movies/603/favorite

### Listar favoritos (paginado)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/movies/favorites?page=0&size=10

### Remover favorito
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/movies/603/favorite

### --- Watch Later ---

### Marcar para assistir depois
POST http://localhost:8080/api/movies/603/watch-later

### --- Actuator ---

### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

### Métricas
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics

### Info
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/info

### --- Swagger ---
### Acesse no browser: http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html
